# AutoDialer Pro - Environment Variables
# Bu faylni /opt/autodialer/.env ga ko'chiring va qiymatlarni to'ldiring
# chmod 600 /opt/autodialer/.env - faqat root o'qiy olsin

# Telegram Bot (MAJBURIY)
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token_here
TELEGRAM_ADMIN_CHAT_ID=your_telegram_chat_id_here

# Nonbor API (MAJBURIY)
NONBOR_API_URL=https://test.nonbor.uz/api/v2/telegram_bot/get-order-for-courier/

# SIP Server (MAJBURIY)
SARKOR_ENDPOINT=sarkor-endpoint
SIP_SERVER=well-tech.sip.uz

# Qo'ng'iroq sozlamalari (IXTIYORIY)
WAIT_BEFORE_CALL=90
MAX_RETRIES=2
TELEGRAM_ALERT_TIME=150
POLLING_INTERVAL=3
CALL_WAIT_TIME=30

# TTS sozlamalari (IXTIYORIY)
TTS_AUDIO_CACHE=/var/lib/autodialer/audio/cache
TTS_ASTERISK_PATH=/usr/share/asterisk/sounds/custom
